# Test fixtures for /speckit.todo command
# Each subdirectory represents a different test scenario:
# - valid/          : Workspace with properly formatted SPECKIT TODO blocks
# - malformed/      : Workspace with broken/incomplete TODO blocks
# - empty/          : Workspace with no TODO blocks
# - negative/       : Workspace with non-SPECKIT TODO comments (should be ignored)
# - oversized/      : Workspace with >10 TODO blocks (tests batching)
